rows.label: qst201410_msg0001
rows.name:
It's all draws. We're not getting
any closer to a winner...

rows.label: qst201410_msg0002
rows.name:
Isn't that Hikari and Zakuro?
Have you two been chatting
here all this time?

rows.label: qst201410_msg0003
rows.name:
We're having a competition to
see who has more Girl Power.

rows.label: qst201410_msg0004
rows.name:
Hey, Mikumari, since you're
here, could you judge for us-

rows.label: qst201410_msg0005
rows.name:
Wait, Hikari. Are you
sure about Mikumari?

rows.label: qst201410_msg0006
rows.name:
I get the impression her Girl
Power isn't that high...

rows.label: qst201410_msg0007
rows.name: Wh-What...

rows.label: qst201410_msg0008
rows.name:
Well, she doesn't seem to have a
very high level of Girl Power.

rows.label: qst201410_msg0009
rows.name:
Wouldn't it be difficult to
ask someone with low Girl
Power like Mikumari to judge?

rows.label: qst201410_msg0010
rows.name:
Hey! Stop saying my Girl
Power is low over and over!

rows.label: qst201410_msg0011
rows.name:
I'm picky about trends,
and I like sweets too!

rows.label: qst201410_msg0012
rows.name: My Girl Power is super high!

rows.label: qst201410_msg0013
rows.name: No way, you're lying!

rows.label: qst201410_msg0014
rows.name:
You never clean up, Mikumari,
so you're always panicking about
not finding this or that.

rows.label: qst201410_msg0015
rows.name:
And at mealtimes, you're
always starving and gobbling
down your food...

rows.label: qst201410_msg0016
rows.name:
That's just... me being a little
lazy, and true to my instincts...

rows.label: qst201410_msg0017
rows.name:
Isn't that what having
low Girl Power means?

rows.label: qst201410_msg0018
rows.name:
Exactly. At the very least, you
should stop jumping into the bath.

rows.label: qst201410_msg0020
rows.name: You two can just say whatever you want!

rows.label: qst201410_msg0021
rows.name:
You're both jerks, Hikari and
Zakuro! I'm done with you!

rows.label: qst201410_msg0022
rows.name:
Uh oh, I think we went
a little too far...

rows.label: qst201410_msg0023
rows.name:
We should take her some
sweets later and apologize.

rows.label: qst201410_msg0024
rows.name: Yeah, let's do that...
